    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to own! This car is in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and weekend trips. It\u2019s been well-loved and looked after, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner right away. If you're looking for a dependable vehicle that still looks and drives great, this is the one for you! Feel free to message me with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home! \u2728",
      "price": 31500.0,
